item.title: Pi command help
item.dc:creator: @spearo spearo
item.description:
@spearo wrote:

Can someone make my tele command, teleport different heights.

if (playerCommand.startsWith("tele")) { String[] arg = playerCommand.split(" "); if (arg.length > 3) c.getPA().startTeleport(Integer.parseInt(arg[1]), Integer.parseInt(arg[2]), Integer.parseInt(arg[3]), "modern"); else if (arg.length == 3) c.getPA().startTeleport(Integer.parseInt(arg[1]), Integer.parseInt(arg[2]), 0, "modern"); }
